Video overview - https://youtu.be/B2kx1ko5CC4

Package in Arduino Preferences - http://arduino.esp8266.com/stable/package_esp8266com_index.json

To SHH -ssh nameofPi@staticIPaddress

mosquitto_sub -h localhost -t "outTopic"

mosquitto_pub -h localhost -t "inTopic" -m "1"
mosquitto_pub -h localhost -t "inTopic" -m "0"

Note:
If you use these commands on your computer (not SSHed), localhost is the static IP for the RPi.

PubSubClient library - https://pubsubclient.knolleary.net
